"Taint.\n"
"\n"
"1: That the Prophet Most Simian demonstrated that monothought begets Proper-"
"Life.\n"
"\n"
"1: That the purpose of Proper-Life is the Expungement of the Taint.\n"
"\n"
"1: That the Arc of Time provides the mortal theater for the Sacred "
"Expungement.\n"
"\n"
"1: That Akatosh is Time is Proper-Life is Taint-Death."
